casebody.data:
PROGRESS MICHIGAN, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
ATTORNEY GENERAL, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158150, 158151
COA: 340921, 340956 Supreme Court of Michigan. August 8, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of plaintiff-appellant to exceed the page limitation for its reply brief is GRANTED. The 12-page reply brief submitted on July 26, 2019, is accepted for filing.
